      <title>英国外长斯塔默将在重要峰会开幕式上承诺将废除繁文缛节</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-13/uk-s-starmer-to-open-key-summit-with-vow-to-rip-up-red-tape</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 将誓言废除阻碍经济增长的监管措施，以期在执政百日的艰难时期缓解国际投资者的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-13/uk-s-starmer-to-open-key-summit-with-vow-to-rip-up-red-tape</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 13 Oct 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡将对涉嫌说谎丑闻的反对党领袖展开审判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-13/singapore-to-start-trial-of-opposition-leader-in-lying-scandal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡反对党领袖因涉嫌说谎将于周一开庭受审，这可能会在明年必须举行的大选之前对其政党进行更严格的审查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-13/singapore-to-start-trial-of-opposition-leader-in-lying-scandal</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 13 Oct 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>社会民主党在立陶宛大选中取得领先</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-13/social-democrats-take-early-lead-in-lithuania-s-general-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[立陶宛社会民主党有望赢得 12 年来的首次议会选举，因为选民转向反对党，希望该党能缩小这个波罗的海国家日益扩大的经济差距。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-13/social-democrats-take-early-lead-in-lithuania-s-general-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 13 Oct 2024 21:08:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普呼吁加大边境特工招聘力度，并提高薪酬</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-13/trump-to-call-for-border-agent-hiring-spree-with-new-pay-hikes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党候选人唐纳德·特朗普呼吁给边境特工加薪并发放奖金，以招募 10,000 名新人来保护美墨边境的安全。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-13/trump-to-call-for-border-agent-hiring-spree-with-new-pay-hikes</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 13 Oct 2024 20:50:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普加州集会附近一名持枪男子被捕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-10-13/urgent-man-with-loaded-gun-arrested-at-checkpoint-near-donald-trump-s-weekend-rally-in-southern-california</link>
      <description><![CDATA[洛杉矶（美联社）——当局称，周六晚上，一名内华达州男子在南加州沙漠​​唐纳德·特朗普集会现场外的安全检查站被捕，他的车里有一把霰弹枪、一把装满子弹的手枪、弹药和几本假护照。他当天以 5,000 美元的保释金获释。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-10-13/urgent-man-with-loaded-gun-arrested-at-checkpoint-near-donald-trump-s-weekend-rally-in-southern-california</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 13 Oct 2024 20:31:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列国防军称，真主党无人机袭击以色列造成四名士兵死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-13/hezbollah-drone-attack-in-israel-injures-67-channel-12-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[真主党在海法南部发动无人机袭击，造成四名以色列士兵死亡，这是自以色列加强对黎巴嫩的攻击以来，对以色列军队最致命的袭击之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-13/hezbollah-drone-attack-in-israel-injures-67-channel-12-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 13 Oct 2024 18:38:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯公布自己的健康记录后，又拿特朗普的病历挑衅他</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-13/harris-slams-lying-about-hurricane-aid-on-north-carolina-trip</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯批评其共和党对手唐纳德·特朗普隐瞒其医疗记录，称他对美国选民不透明。]]></description>
